members.models module

class members.models.Member(*args, **kwargs)[source]

Bases: Model

Class defining the club member fields to be stored in the app database.

Parameters:

  • first_name (str) – Members first name. Max length 25 characters.

  • last_name (str) – Members last name/surname/family name. Max length 50 characters.

  • id_number (str) – Unique ID number of the member. Usually government issued.

  • dob (DateField) – Date of birth of the member.

  • email (EmailField) – Email address of the member.
